title.narrative: Accelerating the Sustainable Control & Elimination of Neglected Tropical Diseases (ASCEND): Lot 1 (Southern Asia and East Africa): Core delivery costs to October 2020, excluding MDA costs.

description.narrative: This activity (Accelerating the Sustainable Control & Elimination of Neglected Tropical Diseases (ASCEND): Lot 1 (Southern Asia and East Africa): Core delivery costs to October 2020, excluding MDA costs.) is a component of Accelerating Sustainable Control and Elimination of Neglected Tropical Diseases (NTDs) - (ASCEND) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £21,340,354. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Basic health care, Infectious disease control. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 01-04-2019 and the end date is 31-03-2022.
